dimensions.name: biz_dt
dimensions.expr: MAX( CASE WHEN ISODOW(strptime(base_dt, '%Y%m%d')) < 6 THEN base_dt ELSE NULL END ) OVER ()
dimensions.label: 최근 영업일

dimensions.name: prev_biz_dt
dimensions.expr: TO_CHAR(   CASE      WHEN EXTRACT(ISODOW FROM TO_DATE(MAX(CASE WHEN EXTRACT(ISODOW FROM TO_DATE(base_dt, 'YYYYMMDD')) < 6 THEN base_dt ELSE NULL END) OVER (), 'YYYYMMDD')) = 1      THEN TO_DATE(MAX(CASE WHEN EXTRACT(ISODOW FROM TO_DATE(base_dt, 'YYYYMMDD')) < 6 THEN base_dt ELSE NULL END) OVER (), 'YYYYMMDD') - INTERVAL '3 DAY'     ELSE TO_DATE(MAX(CASE WHEN EXTRACT(ISODOW FROM TO_DATE(base_dt, 'YYYYMMDD')) < 6 THEN base_dt ELSE NULL END) OVER (), 'YYYYMMDD') - INTERVAL '1 DAY'   END,   'YYYYMMDD' )
dimensions.label: 전영업일
